**** We are a Christian family of four who decided to share our journey with others in hopes to encourage others to not give up in the midst of their storm.
Mike is a pastor of a church based out of California he also provides for his family and is currently in stage 5 kidney failure in need of a kidney. Paulina is a mom
of two who also provides for her family while dealing with some health issues as well. Ethan is a young passionate boy who loves to read and Jer is a
4 year old daddy's girl who is passionate about being a princess and loving fashion. We love meeting new people and going on advantures and most of
all we have a heart for God and souls.